#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/optimize/seo.rst:329
msgid ""
"`Google Page Speed "
"<https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Google pagina snelheid "
"<https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/optimize/seo.rst:331
